        <div class="field__item">

  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_hero/public/2024-03/header_preventing_magnet_meltdowns.jpg?itok=kGVokH4y" width="1600" height="900" alt="Maxim Marchevsky (left) and Soren Prestemon discussing an experimental setup to test the sensitivity of a temperature monitoring system for a high temperature superconducting magnet." />





